Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.03,0:00:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是正正
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.49,0:00:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你看来很有精神呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.08,0:00:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,打倒虚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害 小剑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,八千流
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我要稍微活动下身体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你找个地方去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才有种怀念的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是错觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,非常谢谢 死神先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才的虚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是我家人的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这样大家就能瞑目了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:03:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我更早来这儿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,也许就能保护你的家人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你不该道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不 那是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 我叫荧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不介意的话 您的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫正义
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,追求正义的正义
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,正义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是正正
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,八千流
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是八千流吗 好久不见呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是正正
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来很精神呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 木材这么多够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,有这么多的话就能够撑到早上了 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,金平糖 吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这些给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这些 正正
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不太喜欢吃甜的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,八千流不仅是十一番队的副队长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,还是女子死神协会的会长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,很努力 很棒呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,正正在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,在追那些移动的虚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,四处走动消灭他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,很辛苦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一点也不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有点旅行的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,很适合我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在家里也很无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你家人不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,以前有个妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,以前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,被虚杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那天 因为些无聊的小事吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,还没有和好我就去执行任务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,然后几周后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我终于完成任务回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,至少想道个歉 说声对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,得到她说个没关系原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨虚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,打倒虚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,全部打死 总有一天把杀死我妻子的虚也杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 我和像荧这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:06:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,因为虚而变成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:06:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,悲伤一个的人约定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,要消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的虚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,呀 不小心就耍帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我支持你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,请加油直到消灭最后一只虚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 正正
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,正义先生 很厉害呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,正正
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 他很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,从这里一直往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,就能到八千流之前来的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但是很远…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 我跑得非常快的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你为我带路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,正…正
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是荧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:08:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,荧荧 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,荧荧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,小剑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你砍了这么多呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得正正吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,正正
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说那个正义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 虽然好久没见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他看起来挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你见他了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,八千流
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,见了之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就和好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.10,0:09:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,正正 你吃金平糖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 八千流
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱甜的爱到无可自拔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃 再给我点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,小剑不去也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,劳烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,荧荧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来 正正的妻子做的饭也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么吵架呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,因为些无聊的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那天 那天…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了正正
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,虚的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没感觉到呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,八千流 荧就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,打倒虚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,正正
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶的虚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,正正
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,荧荧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,八千流 荧已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了 我最恨的死神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.09,0:12:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 正义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这边的工作结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,您又要赶往他地了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我的职责就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.11,0:12:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,追击虚将之击败
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我举目无亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不能和您同行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,茧 我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,天黑了 回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.34,0:13:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜 回见了 正正
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.39,0:13:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 八千流小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你可不能太接近正正哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,送到这儿就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.16,0:13:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,正义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.01,0:13:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,茧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,茧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.69,0:14:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你终于来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.11,0:14:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,正义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,放开茧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,放就放开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那个女人已无利用价值了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.26,0:14:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,茧 你无需担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.05,0:14:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我来打败他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,希望不会再让任何人悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,正义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,茧 你愿和我同行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.23,0:14:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我像茧你保证
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我会击倒所有虚直到最后一只为止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那就要速战速决了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,斩魄刀 别让人笑掉大牙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,正正
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你ㄚ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.53,0:15:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,居然敢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.84,0:15:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,正义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.85,0:16:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,别靠近他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.31,0:16:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,茧茧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是警告你 不要接近正正吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.23,0:16:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,八千流 你好晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,搜寻我们的灵压费时了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,已经完事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.12,0:16:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我复仇的对手已荡然无存了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,八千流
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.38,0:16:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,虚已全部被我打败了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.51,0:16:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不是哦 还有一只哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.85,0:16:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,远在天边 近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.27,0:16:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,八千流小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,八千流
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那种东西哪儿都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:16:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,因为 正正你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.36,0:17:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就是虚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么傻话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我哪里是虚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,正正最爱甜食了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,正正 你要吃金平糖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.38,0:17:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了 八千流
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我一见着甜食就没命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.06,0:17:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,正正的心还犹存
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.81,0:17:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你气色不错麻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,一不留神就耍酷了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,正正的心终有一天会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.91,0:17:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,终有一天会变成完完全全的虚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是虚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不是虚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.58,0:17:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:17:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你妻子叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.63,0:18:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,她的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么我想不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是虚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我要向杀害妻子的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,虚复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.44,0:18:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,杀害你妻子的是正正你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.57,0:18:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这 究竟是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,虚 你ㄚ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是你ㄚ干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是我 是我的错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我听小剑说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,正正你去追击虚 被虚附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 在你杀害妻子后 看到映在镜中的正正的意识
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.35,0:18:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,反而控制了虚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 就如你喜欢金平糖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,忘记妻子的名字一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,终有一天 正正的意识也会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样 是我 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.84,0:19:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,八千流
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,茧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我要拉你陪葬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.74,0:19:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,正义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.25,0:20:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,正义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,正正
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,茧 你平安无事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.26,0:20:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我明明向你 保证要将最后一只虚打倒为止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.18,0:20:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.02,0:20:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,无所谓的 无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,正正
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.21,0:20:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好甜好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.63,0:20:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,正正
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.53,0:21:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我会奋战到底
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,希望不会再让任何人悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,0:21:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,完事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.38,0:21:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.92,0:21:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.64,0:21:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你都吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.56,0:21:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,小剑你好温柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.03,0:21:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.04,0:23:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,下集为止单集短篇故事也该结束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.67,0:23:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还得我压轴收尾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.96,0:23:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,黑崎 我准备暂时留在现世了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.09,0:23:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,冬狮郎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.01,0:23:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,有何不便吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.34,0:23:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.93,0:23:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 那就请多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.55,0:23:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我的大活跃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,死神图鉴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,小剑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.84,0:24:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我摘了好多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.55,0:24:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不错 我这边也收获颇丰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.27,0:24:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,都过了好多天了 我们怎么还没到静灵庭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.73,0:24:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们迷路了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.65,0:24:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
